{"tid":698384,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"默克爾紮馬訓示特朗普 全球瘋傳","createTime":"2018-06-11T15:33:46.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-11T19:06:50.000Z","uid":25558,"like":15,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"5372d6728694e14b4bc844a9740a5b44f65732b7","tid":698384,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T15:33:46.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20180611/20416739\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180611%2F20416739&d=MRtWvV%2BhC9yd2w7J3s%2Fj3ghMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=de389c90\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180611%2F20416739&h=06e4c3d2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20180611/20416739</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年06月11日 <br />\n<br />\n默克爾紮馬訓示特朗普<br />\n全球瘋傳<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180611/large/11wf02p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180611%2Flarge%2F11wf02p.jpg&h=3df3d43f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【德國視角】■德發放默克爾跟特朗普對峙的照片，被指最能反映美國與盟友為敵的局面。美聯社<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n常說「有圖有真相」， G7七國官方照片卻拍出七種視角，其中德國的「講數照」被瘋傳，輿論認為最能反映美國與盟友為敵的局面。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n美先發相　德法反擊<br />\n<br />\n這場社交網上的「世界大戰」由美國白宮發言人桑德斯引發，她於加國時間上周六早上10時45分經Twitter發放黑白會議照，相中她「老細」特朗普雙手交叉身體仰後、氣定神閒又帶驕傲，其他國家領袖在他跟前低頭彎腰。10分鐘後，法國總統辦公室發相還擊，總統馬克龍站在中央位置，與背坐着的特朗普交涉，其他領袖亦圍着細心聆聽。<br />\n<br />\n德國政府在IG的發圖被讚最貼近現實，相中總理默克爾有如「大阿姐」俯身按着桌子逼近，其他領袖不是被擋着，就是對特朗普表現不耐煩，特朗普就像個被師長圍攻教訓的學生。意大利、日本和加拿大亦相繼發放會議照，氣氛和構圖相對謙和；只有英國沒加入戰團，首相文翠珊戶口中盡是與眾領袖言笑晏晏的公關照。<br />\n<br />\n美國《時代》周刊/《商業內幕》網站  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180611/large/a1502a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180611%2Flarge%2Fa1502a.gif&h=b8295898&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【美國視角】■美官方會議照顯得其他領袖在特跟前低頭彎腰。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180611/large/a1502b.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180611%2Flarge%2Fa1502b.gif&h=36a65f7b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【法國視角】■法國官方發放的照片把馬克龍放在中央位置。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n 上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n特反口拒撐G7公報　斥杜魯多不誠實　威脅收汽車稅<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n不滿文翠珊像「校長」　特冷淡不提<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不滿文翠珊像「校長」特冷淡不提<br />\n<br />\n特反口拒撐G7公報斥杜魯多不誠實　威脅收汽車稅"},{"pid":"3dd2ae5a1ac090d893718e0877f6b13db470a500","tid":698384,"uid":157362,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T15:34:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"72e7c44eb3ed080d186dadff1af3617529209c7a","tid":698384,"uid":130709,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T15:36:24.000Z","msg":"樓主等俾侵侵d便宜仔咬喇。。。"},{"pid":"c7144d7fbada9a55ad8995fc9fb1dfb411d020c3","tid":698384,"uid":94828,"like":16,"dislike":4,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T15:36:33.000Z","msg":"法國打飛機打到<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"841f1f5790a887da070c13a8be6c6ff5aacb5587","tid":698384,"uid":60219,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T15:37:31.000Z","msg":"法國果張特別柒"},{"pid":"0fc40a14e88a75e1cf63e292ce359776e41fabd6","tid":698384,"uid":24345,"like":7,"dislike":7,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T15:38:56.000Z","msg":"GDP 係德國8,9倍嘅美國被訓示<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85cae181599fca9f728fa206a95e8202f59ab0e8","tid":698384,"uid":71734,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T15:40:17.000Z","msg":"法國人講嘢真係一定要縮埋啲手指<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" 